Package com.cognifide.qa.bb.aem.dialog.configurer

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ComponentConfigurerFactory
    This interface represents a factory of ComponentConfigurer instances.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComponentConfig
    Represents component configuration: name of the component config name actual configuration in form of List<ConfigurationEntry>
    ComponentConfigBuilder
    This builder provides a way to construct manually Component Data Tables.
    ComponentConfigurer
    This class configures components using data tables retrieved from scenarios.
    ConfigurationEntry
    Represents a single row in a data table.
    DialogFieldMap
    This class stores the classes of dialog fields.
    FieldsetConfig
    Represents a single field in a fieldset.
    JsonToComponentConfig
    This class parses component configurations from a JSON file to ComponentConfig
    MultifieldConfig
    Represents a single field in a multifield.
    ScenarioConfigUtils
    Utility for accessing ConfigurationEntry elements.
